#compdef getcap
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Description
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  Completion script for libcap's getcap:
#  - https://people.redhat.com/sgrubb/libcap-ng/
#
# ZSH provides the `zsh/cap` module that does not work on most modern systems,
# in lieu of this I have written this zsh-completion script.
#
# Written by
#  - Zephyr Pellerin (https://github.com/zv)
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

_arguments '*:file:_files'
                '-r[recursive]' \
                '-v[display all entries]' \
                '-h[help]'

# Local variables:
# mode: shell-script
# End:
# ex: sw=2 ts=2 et filetype=sh
